name: JOURNEY
description:
JOURNEY

I'm on my way into a journey to unknown place or result.
On its way, I could possibly found gems,
or  found thorn bushes. 

During those times, there are many decisions that I regret and also decisions that I am proud of. 

This is what I call a journey.
And now I'm still walking the path.
To find where will I stop.

watercolor on cold press paper A3
2126 X 3600 px

Personal use only.
